<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>No need to kill the spectres. Let a buddy with SOW and levitate train them away (4 of them). When the sentry sees that no spectres are around, she believes that you killed them makes a honorful suicide and drops the harpoon for you. :-)) BTW: Its a freeport based quest too. Did it that way. Myself didn´t get hit one time. The druid gated out afterwards and all were happy.</font></td></tr></table>
