<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>There is a second quest that you can do to get this weapon. It is based in the Erudin Deepwater knights guild. It seems that there is a plan to build a bridge from Qeynos to Erudin and the Knights aren't pelased. They want you to hunt down the 3 engineers that are involved and bring back their heads.  There is a gnome, a dwarf and a human involved. Once you hunt them all down and kill them you need to bring back their heads and the plans for the project. AllaKhazam's web site has all the details. Hope this helps all the Palidins out there.</font></td></tr></table>
